org.fest.assertions
Class ByteAssert

java.lang.Object
  org.fest.assertions.ByteAssert

public final class ByteAssert
extends Object

Understands assertion methods for bytes. To create a new instance of this class use the method Assertions.assertThat(byte).

Author:
Yvonne Wang
